### Accent split (light and dark)

| Context | Tokens |
|---------|--------|
| Text, borders, outline/ghost controls on a surface | `--pvc-color-accent`, `--pvc-color-accent-strong` |
| Filled primary actions | `--pvc-color-accent-solid`, `--pvc-color-accent-solid-hover` |
| Outline/ghost destructive | `--pvc-color-danger-strong`, `--pvc-color-danger` (borders via mix) |
| Filled destructive | `--pvc-color-danger-solid`, `--pvc-color-danger-solid-hover` |

In dark mode, **foreground** accents lighten for contrast on dark surfaces; **solid fills** stay saturated so primary and danger buttons remain confident on the canvas.

## Type Scale

```css
--type-meta: 0.75rem;      /* 12px — metadata, hints, grid footnotes */
--type-control: 0.875rem;  /* 14px — labels, buttons, dense UI */
--type-body: 1rem;         /* 16px — body copy */
--type-section: 1.25rem;   /* 20px — section headings */
--type-page: 1.9375rem;    /* 31px — page headings */
```

| Token | px | Tailwind equivalent | Component mapping |
|-------|-----|---------------------|-------------------|
| `--type-meta` | 12 | `text-xs` | Eyebrow, hints, `CopyableValue` meta |
| `--type-control` | 14 | `text-sm` | Labels, buttons, supporting text |
| `--type-body` | 16 | `text-base` | `Pathogen::Typography::Text` |
| `--type-section` | 20 | `text-xl` | `Lead`, section headings |
| `--type-page` | 31 | `text-3xl` (approx.) | `Heading` h1 tier |

**14px and 16px** are the product workhorses. Larger sizes are for hierarchy inside real workflows, not preview decoration.

Implementation preference: `text-[length:var(--type-control)]` in new components. Typography components may continue using Tailwind scale classes where values match exactly.

## Spacing Scale

Pathogen uses Tailwind’s default **4px base**. Semantic spacing is not tokenised — use the scale consistently:

| px | Tailwind | Typical role |
|----|----------|--------------|
| 4 | `1` | Icon padding, tight stacks |
| 8 | `2` | Control internals |
| 12 | `3` | Radio rows, inline groups |
| 16 | `4` | Field gaps, fieldsets |
| 24 | `6` | Section gaps |
| 32 | `8` | Region separation |

## Radius Scale

```css
--pvc-radius-control-sm: 0.125rem; /* 2px */
--pvc-radius-control: 0.25rem;     /* 4px */
--pvc-radius-action: 0.375rem;     /* 6px */
--pvc-radius-panel: 0.5rem;        /* 8px */
```

| Token | px | Components |
|-------|-----|------------|
| `--pvc-radius-control-sm` | 2 | Checkboxes |
| `--pvc-radius-control` | 4 | Inputs, inline code focus |
| `--pvc-radius-action` | 6 | `Button`, `CopyableValue`, tabs |
| `--pvc-radius-panel` | 8 | Data grid frame, preview panels |

Use `rounded-[var(--pvc-radius-*)]` in component class strings rather than hard-coded `rounded-md` / `rounded-lg` when the role is known.

## Elevation

```css
--pvc-shadow-none: none;
--pvc-shadow-overlay: 0 1px 3px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.2);
```

| Level | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Product surfaces | No shadow |
| Grouped regions | Border + surface step |
| Overlays | `--pvc-shadow-overlay` |

## Motion

```css
--pvc-duration-fast: 120ms;
--pvc-duration-default: 160ms;
--pvc-duration-overlay: 200ms;
```

Prefer colour, border, background, and opacity transitions. Reserve movement for overlays. Honour `prefers-reduced-motion`.

## Geometry And Composition

Geometry is expressed through **layout**, not decoration:

- Vertical and horizontal alignment to a shared grid.
- Gutters between primary and secondary work areas.
- Dividers, table rules, and borders that trace real structure.
- Small accent bars or blocks only for navigation, selection, focus, status, or grouping.
- Asymmetric layouts only when workflow priority is genuinely uneven.

## Component-Scoped Tokens

### Data grid (`pvc_datagrid_layer.css`)

Internal tokens such as `--pvc-data-grid-border-color`, `--pvc-data-grid-body-bg`, and cell padding. These reference neutral/primary palette for grid-specific contrast needs. Do not override from host apps unless integrating the grid as a whole.

### Tooltip

`--pvc-tooltip-origin` — placement-based transform origin. Tooltip surface uses `neutral-950` fill with overlay shadow; treat as overlay tier, not canvas surface.

## Migration Status

| Component | Semantic colour | Semantic radius | Type tokens |
|-----------|-----------------|-----------------|-------------|
| `Button` | Yes | `--pvc-radius-action` | via `text-sm` / `text-xs` |
| `CopyableValue` | Yes | `--pvc-radius-action` | `--type-meta` |
| `Typography::*` | Partial (`neutral-*`) | Tailwind utilities | Tailwind scale |
| `Link`, `Tabs`, `Form::*` | Partial | Mixed | `text-sm` labels |
| `DataGridComponent` | Scoped grid tokens | `rounded-lg` ≈ panel | — |
| `Tooltip` | Hard-coded overlay | `rounded-lg` | — |

New and touched components should move toward the `Button` reference pattern.
